subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. This species was previously recorded from Argentina , Guatemala , Peru ( Cusco ), Uruguay ( Montevideo ) and Colombia (La Mesa) (
Savaris et al ., 2016
,
Norrbom et al., 2018
,
Calvo et al ., 2019
). This species also occurs in the departments of Boyacá , Cundinamarca , and Santander .
